sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (Tool)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_011_1_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Remote Start Charging Session – Remote Start First
    Note over CP,CS: Section 3.4.2, Table 130, Page 115-116

    CS->>CP: 1. RemoteStartTransaction.req
